seo: Supervisord,远程命令执行漏洞,inet_http_server,漏洞检测
seo_en: Supervisord, Remote Command Execution Vulnerability, inet_http_server, Vulnerability Detection
summary: 该插件用于检测Supervisord的inet_http_server模块是否存在远程命令执行漏洞，通过构造特定的XML请求并验证DNSLog回显来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether there is a remote command execution vulnerability in the inet_http_server module of Supervisord. It confirms the existence of the vulnerability by constructing specific XML requests and verifying DNSLog callbacks.
